archimate:ApplicationFunction.name: Resource Test rules defining
archimate:ApplicationFunction.documentation: Resource Test Strategy and Policy Management test rules defining functions provide the necessary functionality to manage the local rules that define the strategies for conducting a test. Strategies can range from simple (e.g. - check the status of a router) to complex (e.g. - perform an end-to-end test on a circuit and sectionalize the problem).
